section: Adjusted Model for Truck Parking Analysis
text:
Adjusted Model for Truck Parking Analysis
\[ \Delta\text{Num\_Truck\_Stop}_{t=2006-2016} = \sum_{i=2}^{0} \beta_{t-i} \text{TPA}_{t-i}\cdot \text{Severity}_t \\ + \gamma X_t + \epsilon_t \]

$ _{t-i} $: A lagged dummy variable indicating a severe truck parking accident.
Severity is our measure of severity of the accident (‘VEHICLES_IN_ACCIDENT’ or ‘INJURIES’ or Fatalities)
